00:03:19,858 --> 00:03:21,729
Princess Celestia wanted
me to give her students

33
00:03:21,770 --> 00:03:23,083
a quick overview
on the history

34
00:03:23,101 --> 00:03:24,640
of enchanted objects
in Equestria.

35
