Huh? Oh.

47
00:04:09,243 --> 00:04:11,895
Hey! Twilight and I are
about to head to Canterlot.

48
00:04:12,055 --> 00:04:14,516
Just checking to see if you
need anything before we left.

49
00:04:14,886 --> 00:04:15,840
Nope! Not at all!

50
00:04:15,901 --> 00:04:17,489
I'm good here. Not
good. Great.

51
00:04:17,526 --> 00:04:19,107
Not a problem in
the world.

52
00:04:20,129 --> 00:04:21,440
Uh-huh.

53
00:04:21,636 --> 00:04:24,363
So... what are
you doing exactly?

54
00:04:25,452 --> 00:04:29,581
I was... just trying to decide
which friendship lesson

55
00:04:29,612 --> 00:04:32,147
I was going to tackle while
you two were in Canterlot!

56
00:04:32,972 --> 00:04:36,756
Oh, yup. Right here. Where I
just left them a second ago!

57
00:04:38,492 --> 00:04:41,735
Bake a cake with Pinkie Pie,
scrapbook with Applejack,

58
00:04:41,827 --> 00:04:43,495
sew with Rarity...

59
00:04:43,698 --> 00:04:44,486
Uh.

60
00:04:44,769 --> 00:04:46,756
Help an animal with Fluttershy,

61
00:04:47,083 --> 00:04:51,218
chillax with Rainbow
Dash? What is chillaxing?

62
00:04:51,993 --> 00:04:53,249
No idea.

63
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:56,098
You know, uh, if
you're nervous about

64
00:04:56,116 --> 00:04:59,396
your friendship lessons,
it's totally okay to say so.

65
00:04:59,729 --> 00:05:04,596
NERVOUS?! ME!
HAHAHA. Oh Spike.

66
00:05:04,633 --> 00:05:08,375
You really are hilarious.
You think I'm nervous

67
00:05:08,424 --> 00:05:09,784
that I'm going to
fail something

68
00:05:09,827 --> 00:05:12,301
